channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Even the Media Is Flipping Out About the Total Dysfunction at the DNC
Trump accuses Biden admin of 'MASSIVE SCANDAL' after new jobs numbers dramatically revised downward
item.description: Former President Trump quickly jumped on a massive downward revision by the Labor Department on new job growth, charging that the Biden-Harris administration "PADDED THE NUMBERS."

item.title: London Mayor Fears for Safety If Trump Wins
item.description: London Mayor Sadiq Khan said he's concerned about his safety if Donald Trump wins the U.S. presidential election and that the Labour Party should support the campaign of Kamala Harris, The New Statesman reported.

item.title: Stunning: BLS Announces Largest Downward Revision in Jobs in 15 Years
Bloomberg drops $10 million donation in bid to help House Democrats
item.description: Billionaire Mike Bloomberg threw $10 million behind House Democrats last month, adding to the $20 million he gave to bolster the party's White House efforts.

item.title: Sen. Sanders Praises Harris, Pushes for More Changes
item.description: Sen. Bernie Sanders on Wednesday praised Democrat presidential nominee Kamala Harris and said he would do "everything" possible to get her elected, but also pressed for major policy changes on healthcare, tax reform and affordable housing.

item.title: CNN Contributor Scott Jennings Silences CNN Panel After Giving Them a Much Needed Reality Check
Democratic New Jersey Rep. Bill Pascrell Jr. dead at 87
item.description: Democratic Congressman Bill Pascrell Jr. of New Jersey passed away on Wednesday after serving 14 terms in Congress.

item.title: Nate Silver: Harris to Receive 'Convention Bounce'
item.description: Vice President Kamala Harris' poll numbers will continue to climb after this week's Democratic National Convention, FiveThirtyEight founder Nate Silver said.

item.title: Donald Trump Offers Rare Praise - for Barack Obama?
Obama speech to secure border without 'tearing' kids from parents omits somber DHS report on missing migrants
item.description: Barack Obama when talking about securing the border at the DNC Tuesday omitted a new DHS report citing tens to hundreds of thousands missing migrant children.

item.title: Harris Called for Donations to Abolish ICE Groups
item.description: While serving as the junior senator from California, Democrat presidential nominee and Vice President Kamala Harris called for donations to groups that seek to abolish Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE) and Customs and Border Protection (CBP).

item.title: Study Shows the Lengths Media Is Having to Go to Make Kamala Harris Look Good
Gavin Newsom says Kamala Harris will have 'more time to articulate nuances' after the DNC
item.description: California Gov. Gavin Newsom told Fox News' Peter Doocy on Tuesday night that Vice President Kamala Harris will have "more time" to lay out her policy positions following the Democratic National Convention.

item.title: Trump Chides White House on Revision of Jobs Report
item.description: Former President Donald Trump on Wednesday accused the Biden administration of "fraudulently manipulating" statistics after the government announced revised job growth numbers for this year showing lower growth than previously reported.
